text: The 1992 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1992 NCAA Division I-A football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by third-year head coach George Chaump. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Category:1992 in sports in Maryland
